Introduction

C.LiTZ is a South Korean live idol duo under RoDa Ent. They had their debut live on August 8th, 2021, and released their first mini album ‘MiDNiGHT STRAYER’ on January 6th 2022.

The name C.LiTZ is a combination of claw and blitz, and the period in their name is a reference to the now defunct cover group C.yndrome, which both members were previously a part of.
